+### BUG-046: stdio transport incompatible with launchd — infinite restart loop | Milestone: 0.8 | FIXED
+- **Location:** `src/graph/mcp-server.js`, `.mcp.json`, `.gemini/settings.json`, `scripts/mbo-start.sh`
